data.text: @Kellander68 @POTUS @VP @USPS Since you and I live in the same county, that has to be the case. Still curious about all the very different expiration dates, though.
@wemeow2 @POTUS @VP @USPS They must have contracted from whomever agreed to supply. Mine arrived almost 2 wx ago, is a different brand and exp in Jan 2023! https://t.co/v4Tai9AriB
@geemarcia @ElaineSanfey @MuellerKristine You also got five tests when it was supposed to be four. Maybe they had different suppliers in different areas of the country.

@MuellerKristine @ElaineSanfey @geemarcia I thought it was interesting in the instructions that you’re supposed to check the results at 20 minutes, but don’t bother after 30. Maybe the ingredients are potentially sensitive to time, but not always?

@ElaineSanfey @MuellerKristine @geemarcia I wondered what the difference is, or why they expire at all?
@MuellerKristine @wemeow2 @geemarcia That's a bit crap in both cases. The ones I've bought here recently don't expire until 2023.
